text: Thibault Jaques (born 29 March 1988) is a French professional footballer who plays as a defender for FC Chambly in the French Ligue 2. ==Professional career== Jaques joined FC Chambly in 2016, and captained them to their first ever promotion to the Ligue 2 in 2015. He made his professional debut with Chambly in a 1–0 Ligue 2 win over Valenciennes FC on 26 July 2019, scoring the game winning goal and the first ever for Chambly in the division. ==References== ==External links== * * * Foot National Profile Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:People from Talence Category:French footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:FC Chambly players Category:SR Colmar players Category:US Boulogne players Category:Ligue 2 players Category:Championnat National players Category:Championnat National 2 players
